beer.beer_description: Feels Good To Be Home is a new IPA brewed in our house style with Mosaic, Mosaic LUPOMAX, Motueka and Cryo Pop™.  It pours a light yellow colour with a deep haze. On the nose we cop sherbet, bubblegum and peach which translates well into absolutely popping flavours of lychee, peach, berries and orange sherbet. The finish is soft and lush with a saturating hop wave.
